comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check 2026-07-13: all-status review found context packing and deps visualization items but no single agent story joining bounded lineage,impact,blockers,and evidence traversal; it belongs under pm-96h7."
body: "## User story\n\nAs a coding or planning agent, I want one bounded and explainable relationship query for an item so that I can understand its purpose, execution order, downstream impact, and supporting evidence without guessing or loading unrelated history.\n\n## Token contract\n\nReturn the smallest useful summary first: item identity, state, immediate typed edges, critical path or blockers, evidence pointers, omitted counts, and a continuation token. Expand only on explicit demand or relevance thresholds.\n\n## Explainability contract\n\nEvery included node and edge carries a concise selection reason, source, age or freshness, and whether it is authoritative, inferred, approximate, or user-authored."
